CompatibilityReportCatalog.ReportHeaderText:
General information about using mods: - Never (un)subscribe to anything while the game is running! This resets some mods. - Always exit to desktop and restart the game. NEVER exit to main menu! - Mods not updated for a while might still work fine. Check their Workshop page. - Mod compatible, but not working? Try unsubscribe and resubscribe (while not in game).
Found a mistake? Please fill out this form: https://forms.gle/PvezwfpgS1V1DHqA9
